  'c2440b10-ce63-4d8a-a232-6406605aa1b9', 2012, '1.1', '2012practice-1.1', 'Responding to the view that today''s teenagers are far too materialistic',
  'Group Discussion', 'A newspaper''s letters to the editor',
  '["Teens far too materialistic\nI think that today''s teenagers have a very casual attitude towards material possessions. From the time they are born,they get what they want,even things that are not necessary.And yet they keep demanding more from their parents. It makes no sense to buy things without thinking about the price. What''s more, youngsters are easily affected by their peers. If their friends have something new and trendy, they will also want to have it. But they do not consider whether they really need it. Parents should not buy their children too many items that they do not really need. And they should teach them to treasure what they have. They have to set a good example. Young people need to exercise self-control.\nY.L."]'::jsonb,
  '["whether teenagers are materialistic", "whether teenagers are easily affected by their peers", "how young children should be educated not to be materialistic", "anything else you think is important"]'::jsonb,
  '[{"text": "What do teenagers buy that they do not need?", "number": 1, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "What should children spend their money on?", "number": 2, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "What new things do teens all want to have?", "number": 3, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "How can parents teach their children not to become so materialistic?", "number": 4, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Why do young people want to buy brand name products?", "number": 5, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "What problems can result from becoming too materialistic?", "number": 6, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Why do some parents give in to their children''s demands?", "number": 7, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "How can teenagers develop more self-control over their spending?", "number": 8, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}]'::jsonb,
  '2026-02-11T16:18:37.673069+00:00', '2026-02-11T16:18:37.673069+00:00'
);
